Major ward


.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Major ward -- places an explosive rune on an object
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Major ward places an explosive rune on an object.  The rune will 
explode when the next person tries to steal the object.  You 
need a holy symbol to perform this ritual.

.EP


